CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 24, 1959, pg. 22 reads: "Cage Scramble - Roger Parrish, Westinghouse High School guard, battles for a rebound in a City League game against South High on the latter's court last Friday. Other Westinghouse players in picture are Anthony Liscio (35) and Andrien Page.  The Bulldogs won. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Two referees with Westinghouse and South High School basketball players, playing on Westinghouse gymnasium for City League game
